# Container app
| Component | Unit | Price (CHF) | Notes |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| vCPU (active) | per second | 0.0000192 | Charged while container is processing |
| Memory (active) | per GiB-second | 0.0000024 | Charged while processing |
| Idle Mode | per second | 0.0000024 | Charged if min replicas > 0 |
| Requests | per 1 million requests | 0.319 | First 2M/month are free |
| Free grants | 180,000 vCPU-sec + 360,000 GiB-sec + 2M req | Free | Enough for small workloads |


# Calling ACS (All in CHF)
| Component | CHF Price | Notes |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Swiss Geographic Number Lease | 0.80 CHF/month | Per phone number |
| Inbound Call (Receive) | 0.0080 CHF/min | Per incoming minute |
| Outbound Call (Make) | ~0.0186 CHF/min+ | If your system calls out |
| Call Recording | ~0.0013 CHF/min | Optional |
| Audio Streaming | ~0.0026 CHF/min | Optional |
